publisher			iPi Soft 						
desc_long								关于这款软件							iPi Recorder is a software program provided by iPi Soft for capturing, playing back and processing video records from multiple cameras and depth sensors. Captured records can be used for motion tracking in iPi Mocap Studio.iPi Recorder supports the following cameras and depth sensors: Sony Playstation Eye Microsoft Kinect for Windows / Kinect XBOX 360 ASUS Xtion / Xtion Live Any DirectShow compatible web camerasKey Features Technology: Optical Markerless  Number of cameras: 1 or 2 Kinect (or ASUS Xtion) depth sensors or 3 to 6 Sony PlayStation Eye cameras  Output Format: *.iPiVideo Video Recording Conditions and Environment:      - Indoor and Outdoor     - Normal Lighting Conditions      - No Markers Required  Actor Clothing Requirements:      - actor Can Wear Reasonable Casual clothes.    - Tight-fitting solid-color clothes recommended.   - Jeans and T-shirts are supported.						
